Siya ay naging

475
00:34:30,429 --> 00:34:31,030
napunit

476
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:33,040
at kinakain ng kanyang uri.

477
00:34:36,810 --> 00:34:38,639
Patayin siya! Huwag mo akong pansinin!

478
00:34:39,290 --> 00:34:41,480
Walang aalis dito ng buhay ngayong gabi!

479
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:43,449
Ayokong masaktan ka.

480
00:34:45,469 --> 00:34:46,840
Wala akong choice.

481
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:55,400
Ikaw...

482
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:59,490
Ikaw at ang iyong angkan
ayoko nang mabuhay?

483
00:35:00,670 --> 00:35:03,360
Gusto kitang patayin

484
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,480
para lang mabuhay ang angkan ko.

485
00:35:12,690 --> 00:35:14,480
Patay na si Baze.

486
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:16,800
Baze,

487
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,360
pasensya na po.

488
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:22,070
Hindi kita hahayaang mamatay ng walang kabuluhan.

489
00:35:31,950 --> 00:35:34,010
Hindi na ako mananakot sayo.

490
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,150
Lahat ng ito

491
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:38,710
tapos na!

492
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,920
Patayin mo ako,

493
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:49,620
at hinding hindi mo makukuha
ang antidote para sa Blood on Snow.

494
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:51,230
Ang Hari ng Lingyue ay mamamatay.

495
00:35:52,530 --> 00:35:54,010
Mamamatay din si Zhuge Yue.

496
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:02,140
Mamamatay ka rin!

497
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,110
kamusta ka na?

498
00:36:36,690 --> 00:36:37,560
Zhuge Yue,

499
00:36:40,090 --> 00:36:41,650
W-wala na akong utang sayo.

500
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,100
Lingyue.

501
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:45,920
Chu Qiao...

502
00:36:47,190 --> 00:36:47,920
ay...

503
00:36:49,240 --> 00:36:50,630
sa panulat ng alipin.

504
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:51,910
Iligtas mo siya dali.

505
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,550
Ayokong may utang na loob sa kanya.

506
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:11,840
Aalis na ako sa clan ko

507
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,880
sa iyo upang protektahan.

508
00:37:16,630 --> 00:37:17,510
pangako ko sayo.

509
00:37:19,170 --> 00:37:20,170
Zhuge Yue,

510
00:37:22,770 --> 00:37:24,730
pwede mo ba akong yakapin?

511
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:18,710
Gagawin mo lahat

512
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:23,360
ilibing kasama ko.

513
00:40:34,010 --> 00:40:35,840
Lahat ay umatras sa labas ng panloob na palasyo!

514
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:36,900
Patayin ang mga trespassers!

515
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:38,070
Xing.

516
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,960
Natatakot ako sa pagkakataong ito,

517
00:40:40,070 --> 00:40:42,130
buhay at kamatayan ang tunay na maghihiwalay sa atin.

518
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:43,040
Huan Huan.

519
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:45,000
Nawalan ako ng Great Yan.

520
00:40:45,490 --> 00:40:46,950
Maaari mo ba akong tulungang maibalik ito?

521
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:49,480
Ang pinakamabilis na paraan para palamig siya

522
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,760
ay ilubog ang kanyang buong katawan sa tubig ng yelo.

523
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,510
Lagi mo akong pinoprotektahan.

524
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:54,190
Ngayon,

525
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,000
turn ko na para protektahan ka.

